type: TS LF Trading Bot Error - Execution Unexpected Error

definition.text: An Uncexpected Error occured while procesing the execution of orders. The LF Trading Bot continued running after reporting this error.

paragraphs.text: This error cause the sequence of steps to be taken to be halted.
